absorption:
When a 70 mg subcutaneous bolus injection is given to healthy subjects, the absolute bioavailability is 95%. Accumulation does not occur following daily subcutaneous doses. 
Tmax, SubQ, 1-2 mg/kg, healthy subjects = 3-7 hours;
Cmax, SubQ, 3 mg/kg once daily, NOMID patients = 3628 ng/mL.

